    "comp_side_by_side_t7QNiP": {
      "type": "comp-side-by-side",
      "blocks": {
        "column_CnbnKW": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What is Reviv?",
            "text": "<p>Reviv is a flat-plane, non-locking jaw-supportive oral appliance designed for adult sleep use. Its design maintains stable vertical jaw height without locking the bite, allowing natural jaw micro-movement during sleep.</p><p>Many people find consistent nightly use gradually reduces morning jaw tightness and clenching sensation over weeks to months. Individual experiences vary.</p>",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/image_73.webp",
            "layout": "column-reverse"
          }
        },
        "column_tfXFbt": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What is Oralift?",
            "text": "<p>Oralift is a <strong>wellness-focused device</strong> developed to gently increase your “freeway space” which is the gap between your upper and lower teeth at rest. By doing this, it stimulates your facial muscles to adapt, triggering a <em>Mechano Growth Factor (MGF)</em> healing cascade that supports natural tissue repair.<br/>Oralift is worn for short, prescribed sessions, not necessarily every night, making it a low-maintenance tool for long-term facial rejuvenation.</p>",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/logo_oralift.webp",
            "layout": "column-reverse"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "column_CnbnKW",
        "column_tfXFbt"
      ],
      "name": "Comparison Side By Side",
      "settings": {
        "color_scheme": "scheme-309f11fb-a7c3-4ae0-a1b0-473a4f43ce02",
        "padding_top": 36,
        "padding_bottom": 36
      }
    },
